        <h1>Adventures in fire island</h1>
        <img src="Park.jpg" alt="Fire island National Park">

        <p>Welcome to my blog where is share my unforgetable experience at Fire island.
        Fire island is located at the coastal province of Kenya where there was a lot of adventures to embark on for the beautiful oceans to the diverse restaurants.
        With activities such a scuba diving,kite surfing,snokerling and boat rides to various islands.
        We got to visit certain historical sites in various town that were about three hours away.
        The trip to the various sites was captivating from the eye catching views along the road to the sites themselves that were rich in history.
        I would definetley reccomend staying in this place.
        </p>
